<li><a href="http://www.cs.earlham.edu/~joshh/cgi-bin/geo/utm2ll.html" class="external autonumber" title="http://www.cs.earlham.edu/~joshh/cgi-bin/geo/utm2ll.html" rel="nofollow">[5]</a> UTM to Latitude/Longitude Bulk Converter &lt;--Checked against known values for UTM/LAT-LONG. Appears accurate.</li>
<li><a href="http://www.mundivideo.com/coordinates.htm" class="external text" title="http://www.mundivideo.com/coordinates.htm" rel="nofollow">Get the UTM coordinates of any places in the World</a></li>
